public abstract class RdfObject
extends java.lang.Object

The abstract class from which all of the parsed entities will inherit from General idea is that each section that is parsed will be represented as some class that inherits form this class enabling us at the end to generate the RDF based input file that will be given to the Java Layer for parsing
